{
  "stem": "14810.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[CRYING] And he discouraged me from that and I discouraged him from that too.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we survived till the end.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then add to my misfortune, and I have to tell you that on August the 20th, the American bombed Buna.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You see, Buna was a tremendous-- the IG farm industry had a tremendous complex there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's what we did, the work for the IG farm industry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They made synthetics and all kind of things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That's what we worked in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "August the 20th, the American bombed, bombed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was on a Sunday, I never forget it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And you know, the Germans, they had bunkers right there around there and any time an alarm sounded, they went to the bunkers.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We had to stay right in the warehouse.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were working in a building.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I remember that the American bombers came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There must have been about 200 of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "This was the first-- we heard alarms before that, but they never came there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And this time, they came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I remember when, when the alarm sounded, we had to leave the work and we had to go into the buildings.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And most of all we were happy because we didn't have to work and everybody laid down.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I remember the first time when I could hear-- it was after an hour, we laid on the cement floor and everybody was joking, laughing.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then all of sudden he could hear heavy flak-- you know, they had flak on the aircraft.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Something, instinct, told me that this time it's for real.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It's not like last, last few times.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And the closer their planes got, they could hear their flak got heavier, heavy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And then you could hear the planes, woo, woo.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It was from the distance.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
